<pb n="0164a" id="I01.0065.0164a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 65</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>宋敬業等造塔記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a01"/><p id="pI01p0164a0101">曦望晷速。三曜不停。春還秋往。陰陽<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">貿</unclear><note n="0164001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30634;＝遷【史】</note><app n="0164001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30634;</rdg></app>。有始
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a02"/>將終。有生必滅。唯&CB07099;上大覺。<note n="0164002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00816;＝體【史】</note><app n="0164002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00816;</rdg></app>宿常湛。故使人
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a03"/>知覆護。勿識皈依。是乃佛弟子　宋敬業。崔<note n="0164003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13426;＝海【史】</note><app n="0164003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">海</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13426;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a04"/>寶。郭小德。張<note n="0164004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01739;＝燕【史】</note><app n="0164004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">燕</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01739;</rdg></app>子等。洞識苦空。<note n="0164005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30751;＝淵【史】</note><app n="0164005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30751;</rdg></app>知八解。兼識
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a05"/>財稱不<note n="0164006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30952;＝聚【史】</note><app n="0164006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30952;</rdg></app>。身名假合。見<note n="0164007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30953;＝蘆【史】</note><app n="0164007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蘆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30953;</rdg></app>葦之空虛。知<note n="0164008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30954;＝芭【史】</note><app n="0164008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">芭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30954;</rdg></app>蕉之
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a06"/>匪實。何以逢除厚彰。輕<note n="0164009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30955;＝拔【史】</note><app n="0164009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30955;</rdg></app>&CB07099;明。方欲寄<note n="0164010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30956;＝煎【史】</note><app n="0164010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">煎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30956;</rdg></app>三毒
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a07"/>之苦。永入解脫之門。因茲勝地。建&CB07099;上之功。
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a08"/>大齊天保九年歲次戊寅三月甲午<note n="0164011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30957;＝朔【史】</note><app n="0164011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30957;</rdg></app>六日癸
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a09"/><note n="0164012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30958;＝亥【史】</note><app n="0164012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30958;</rdg></app>。仰為廣固南寺大眾等。敬造寶塔一<note n="0164013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30959;＝區【史】</note><app n="0164013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30959;</rdg></app>。万刃
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a10"/>名山。峭崿峙其北。清<note n="0164014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30510;＝淵【史】</note><app n="0164014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30510;</rdg></app>淥池。遄流<note n="0164015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30934;＝旋【史】</note><app n="0164015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30934;</rdg></app>其前。神仙之
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a11"/>宮詎得方其麗。踴出鑽天可以比其暉。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">崇</unclear>斯<note n="0164016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">稫＝福【史】</note><app n="0164016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">福</lem><rdg wit="【原】">稫</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a12"/>□仰資七世。儗入閑門。龍登<note n="0164017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08660;＝初【史】</note><app n="0164017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">初</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08660;</rdg></app>會。<app source="0164009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30955;</rdg></app>潤現存。超
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a13"/>□□位。　帝祚長<note n="0164018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30741;＝延【史】</note><app n="0164018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">延</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30741;</rdg></app>。法界蒙澤。<note n="0164019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">茖＝若【史】</note><app n="0164019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">茖</rdg></app>不刊石流芳。
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a14"/>□□易滅。其頌曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a15"/>□灼法炬。晃朗慧日。悟<note n="0164020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30819;＝彼【史】</note><app n="0164020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30819;</rdg></app>迷徒。出茲闇室。門稱
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a16"/>不二。義唯歸一。位登&CB07099;上。果緣周畢。麗同玉室。
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a17"/>□似銀宮。彫曦漏月。鐸嚮從風。將如地踊。<app source="0164019" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">茖</rdg></app>現
<lb ed="C I" n="0164a18"/>空中。恃斯勝善。同履虛沖。</p>
